{%- comment -%}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SECTION: Make Payment
DESCRIPTION:
  - Multi-payment instruction section allowing customers to choose payment
    method and view dynamic instructions for each method.
  - Supports Interac e-Transfer, Bank Payment, and Credit Card/PayPal form.
  - Each block renders its own UI layout and unique fields based on block type.

LOGIC OVERVIEW:
  - Section loads external JS: make-payment.js (handles checkbox logic,

  - Renders payment blocks depending on block.type:
        • interac → static informational list + bank icons
        • bank → static list + dynamic loop for bank icons
        • card → credit card/PayPal form + validation
  - Only one payment method can be selected at a time (managed in JS).

DEPENDENCIES:
  - CSS:
      • make-payment.css (custom styling for payment UI)
  - JS:
      • make-payment.js (checkbox toggle logic, validation)
  - Snippets:
      • make-payment-error (form error icon)
      • section-margin (layout spacing system)

FILES UPDATED / ADDED:
  - Added:
      • assets/make-payment.css
      • assets/make-payment.js
  - Updated:
      • This section’s markup defines 3 block layouts with condition checks.

SCHEMA OVERVIEW:
  - Section Settings:
      • title (section heading)
      • full section margin controls (desktop + mobile)
  - Blocks:
      • interac → heading, description, labels/values, up to 5 icons
      • bank → subheading, small text, labels/values, up to 5 bank icons
      • card → heading, card icon, and form fields (JS validated)
  - Preset:
      • "Make Payment"

NOTES:
  - Follows internal Shopify theme standards: naming, spacing, schema grouping.
  - Fully OS2.0 compatible with block-based structure.
  - All images use Shopify's responsive img_url filters.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{%- endcomment -%}


<script src='{{ 'make-payment.js' | asset_url }}' defer='defer'></script>
{{- 'make-payment.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag -}}
{%- style -%}
	{% render 'section-margin' %}
{%- endstyle -%}
<div class="make-payment">
    <div class="container">
        {% if section.settings.title != blank %}
          <h2 class="section-title">{{ section.settings.title }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
            <div class="payment-section">
                {% for block in section.blocks %}
                    {% if block.type == 'interac' %}
                        <!-- BLOCK 1 -->
                        <div class="payment-block">
                            <div class="payment-block-header">
                                <div class="checkbox-group">
                                    <input type="checkbox" name="payment">
                                    <div class="payment-group">
                                    <span class="icon icon-checkmark"></span>
                                    <span>{{ block.settings.heading }}</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="payment-fields">
                           {% if block.settings.description != blank %} <h5>{{ block.settings.description }}</h5> {% endif %}
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                {% if block.settings.label_1 != blank %} <span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_1 }}</span>{% endif %}
                                {% if block.settings.value_1 != blank %} <span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_1 }}</span>{% endif %}
                                </li>

                                <li>
                                 {% if block.settings.label_2 != blank %} <span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_2 }}</span>{% endif %}
                                 {% if block.settings.value_2 != blank %} <span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_2 }}</span>{% endif %}
                                </li>

                                <li>
                                {% if block.settings.label_3 != blank %} <span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_3 }}</span>{% endif %}
                                {% if block.settings.value_3 != blank %} <span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_3 }}</span>{% endif %}
                                </li>

                                <li>
                                {% if block.settings.label_4 != blank %} <span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_4 }}</span>{% endif %}
                                {% if block.settings.value_4 != blank %} <span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_4 }}</span>{% endif %}
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="bank-icons">
                                {% if block.settings.icon_1 %}
                                <div class="bank-icon-inner">
                                <img src="{{ block.settings.icon_1 | img_url:width:100 }}">
                                </div>
                                {% endif %}

                                {% if block.settings.icon_2 %}
                                <div class="bank-icon-inner">
                                <img src="{{ block.settings.icon_2 | img_url:width:100 }}">
                                </div>
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if block.settings.icon_3 %}
                                <div class="bank-icon-inner">
                                <img src="{{ block.settings.icon_3 | img_url:width:100 }}">
                                </div>
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if block.settings.icon_4 %}
                                <div class="bank-icon-inner">
                                <img src="{{ block.settings.icon_4 | img_url:width:100 }}">
                                </div>
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if block.settings.icon_5 %}
                                <div class="bank-icon-inner">
                                <img src="{{ block.settings.icon_5 | img_url:width:100 }}">
                                </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if block.type == 'bank' %}
                    <!-- BLOCK 2 -->
                    <div class="payment-block through-bank">
                        <div class="payment-block-header">
                        <div class="checkbox-group">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="payment">
                            <div class="payment-group">
                            <span class="icon icon-checkmark"></span>
                            <span>{{ block.settings.heading }}</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="payment-fields">
                        <h5 class="block-sub-heading">{{ block.settings.subheading }}</h5>
                        <p class="text-desc">{{ block.settings.small }}</p>
                        <h5>{{ block.settings.description }}</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>{% if block.settings.label_1 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_1 }}</span> {% endif %} {% if block.settings.value_1 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_1 }}</span></li> {% endif %} 
                            <li>{% if block.settings.label_2 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_2 }}</span> {% endif %} {% if block.settings.value_2 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_2 }}</span></li>  {% endif %}
                            <li>{% if block.settings.label_3 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_3 }}</span> {% endif %} {% if block.settings.value_3 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_3 }}</span></li>  {% endif %}
                            <li>{% if block.settings.label_4 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_4 }}</span> {% endif %} {% if block.settings.value_4 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_4 }}</span></li>  {% endif %}
                            <li>{% if block.settings.label_5 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-left">{{ block.settings.label_5 }}</span> {% endif %} {% if block.settings.value_5 != blank %}<span class="payment-text-right">{{ block.settings.value_5 }}</span></li>  {% endif %}
                        </ul>
                        <div class="bank-icons">
                                {% for i in (1..5) %}
                                    {% assign icon_key = "icon_bank_" | append: i %}
                                    {% assign icon = block.settings[icon_key] %}
                                    {% if icon %}
                                      <div class="bank-icon-inner">
                                          <img src="{{ icon | img_url: '200x' }}">
                                      </div>
                                    {% endif %}
                                {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if block.type == 'card' %}
                    <!-- BLOCK 3 -->
                    <div class="payment-block through-cards">
                        <div class="payment-block-option">
                            <div class="payment-block-header">
                            <div class="checkbox-group">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="payment">
                                <div class="payment-group">
                                <span class="icon icon-checkmark"></span>
                                <span>{{ block.settings.heading }}</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-icons">
                            {% if block.settings.card_icon %}
                                <img class="payment-card-icons" src="{{ block.settings.card_icon | img_url: '300x' }}">
                            {% endif %}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <form action="#">
                        <div class="payment-fields">
                            <div class="fieldset name-group">
                            <div class="form-fname">
                                <div class="field">
                                <label>First Name *</label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="FIRST NAME" name="first-name" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="error-message" style="display: none;">
                                <span class="error-icon">{% render 'make-payment-error' %}</span>
                                THIS FIELD IS REQUIRED
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-lname">
                                <div class="field">
                                <label>Last Name *</label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="LAST NAME" name="last-name" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="error-message" style="display: none;">
                                <span class="error-icon">{% render 'make-payment-error' %}</span>
                                THIS FIELD IS REQUIRED
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="field">
                            <label>E-mail *</label>
                            <input type="email" placeholder="E-MAIL" name="email" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="error-message" style="display: none;">
                            <span class="error-icon">{% render 'make-payment-error' %}</span>
                            THIS FIELD IS REQUIRED
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="field">
                                <label>Invoice Number *</label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="INVOICE NUMBER" name="shipping-address" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="error-message" style="display: none;">
                                <span class="error-icon">{% render 'make-payment-error' %}</span>
                                THIS FIELD IS REQUIRED
                            </div>
                            <div class="field">
                                <label>Invoice Amount *</label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="$" name="shipping-address" required>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <button type="button" class="payment-submit button button--secondary focus-inset">
                            <span>submit</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
    </div>
</div>
